com.ibm.ccl.soa.deploy.os
Interface AIXOperatingSystem

All Superinterfaces:
com.ibm.ccl.soa.deploy.core.Capability, com.ibm.ccl.soa.deploy.core.DeployModelObject, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, OperatingSystem
All Known Implementing Classes:
AIXOperatingSystemImpl
public interface AIXOperatingSystem
extends OperatingSystem

A representation of the model object 'AIX Operating System'.

The following features are supported:

  • Desktop
  • Install Date
  • Kernel
  • Last Boot Up Time
  • Owner
  • TCB

See Also:
OsPackage.getAIXOperatingSystem()
